    <subfield code="a">21 pages, standard LaTeX file. 11 Figures (not included) available upon request (hard copy or Postscript (10 Mb)) by e-mail to: pettini@sc2a.unige.ch or pettini@fi.infn.it</subfield>
    <subfield code="9">arXiv</subfield>
